<h1> <%=@game.player.name%> vs AIbot!! </h1>
<h2> What do you choose?!</h2>
<form action="/selection" method="post">
  <input type="image"  src="/img/rock.png" name ="take_your_pick" value="Rock" alt="Rock" />
  <input type="image"  src="/img/paper.png" name ="take_your_pick" value="Paper" alt="Paper" />
  <input type="image"  src="/img/scissors.png" name ="take_your_pick" value="Scissors" alt="Scissors" />
  <input type="image"  src="/img/spock.png" name ="take_your_pick" value="Spock" alt="Spock" />
  <input type="image"  src="/img/lizard.png" name ="take_your_pick" value="Lizard" alt="Lizard" />
</form>

<h3> Quick reminder: </h3>
<ul>
<li> <strong> Rock </strong> crushes scissors and lizard, but gets smothered by paper and vaporised by Spock</li>
<li> <strong> Paper </strong> smothers rock and disproves Spock, but gets cut by scissors and eaten by lizard</li>
<li><strong> Scissors </strong> cuts paper and decapitates lizard, but gets crushed by rock and smashed by Spock </li>
<li><strong> Spock </strong> smashes scissors and vaporises rock, but is disproved by paper and poised by lizard </li>
<li><strong> Lizard </strong> eats paper and poinsons Spock, but is crushed by rock and decapitated by lizard </li>
</ul>

